.TH "devm_platform_ioremap_resource" 9 "devm_platform_ioremap_resource" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
devm_platform_ioremap_resource \- call devm_ioremap_resource() for a platform device
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void __iomem *" devm_platform_ioremap_resource
.BI "(struct platform_device *pdev "  ","
.BI "unsigned int index "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pdev" 12
platform device to use both for memory resource lookup as well as
resource management
.IP "index" 12
resource index
.SH "RETURN"
a pointer to the remapped memory or an \fBERR_PTR\fP encoded error code
on failure.
